OL,3,CHundreds of unique Bronze Age items
OL,4,Cfound by detectorist saved for nation
OL,6,FThese include a number of unique
OL,7,Fartefacts. The function of many of the
OL,8,Fitems is not yet understood, and
OL,9,Fexperts believe it could transform our
OL,10,Funderstanding of Bronze Age Scotland.
OL,12,FExperts also say the hoard highlights
OL,13,FScotland's position in an
OL,14,Finternational network of communities
OL,15,Facross the North Sea, pointing to two
OL,16,F"rattle pendants" which are the first
OL,17,Fever found in Scotland.
