OL,3,CHundreds of unique Bronze Age items
OL,4,Cfound by detectorist saved for nation
OL,6,FThese interlinked bronze rings and
OL,7,Fpendant plates, which would have hung
OL,8,Ffrom a horse or vehicle and rattled as
OL,9,Fthey moved, are usually found in
OL,10,FDenmark, northern Germany and northern
OL,11,FPoland.
OL,13,FThe hoard also includes a sword still
OL,14,Finside a wooden scabbard, bronze
OL,15,Fbuttons looped onto cords, and the
OL,16,Funusually well-preserved remains of
OL,17,Fcomplex decorative straps.
