OL,3,CHundreds of unique Bronze Age items
OL,4,Cfound by detectorist saved for nation
OL,6,FThe hoard has now been acquired by
OL,7,FNational Museums Scotland, and efforts
OL,8,Fare underway to secure funding for
OL,9,Fresearch and conservation of this
OL,10,F"exceptional" find.
OL,12,FMatthew Knight, senior curator of
OL,13,Fprehistory at National Museums
OL,14,FScotland, said: "The Peebles Hoard is
OL,15,Fexceptional, an utterly unique
OL,16,Fdiscovery that rewrites our
OL,17,Funderstanding of both Bronze Age
OL,18,Fcommunities in Scotland and our
OL,19,Fprehistoric international connections.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@MO]vD@QOU
