OL,3,CHundreds of unique Bronze Age items
OL,4,Cfound by detectorist saved for nation
OL,6,FAfter being reported as a Treasure
OL,7,FTrove to National Museum Scotland the
OL,8,Fhoard was excavated from the ground in
OL,9,Fa single block of earth, and analysed
OL,10,Funder laboratory conditions.
OL,12,FThe entire block of earth was CT
OL,13,Fscanned at a specialist imaging
OL,14,Ffacility at the University of
OL,15,FSouthampton, which captured details of
OL,16,Fthe internal structure of the hoard.
