OL,3,CHundreds of unique Bronze Age items
OL,4,Cfound by detectorist saved for nation
OL,6,FThe scanning process also showed some
OL,7,Fof the objects in the hoard had been
OL,8,Fmade using "lost-wax casting", which
OL,9,Fexperts say represents some of the
OL,10,Fearliest evidence of the use of this
OL,11,Fprocess in Scotland.
OL,13,FProfessor Ian Sinclair, founder of the
OL,14,F-VIS X-ray Imaging Centre at the
OL,15,FUniversity of Southampton where the
OL,16,Fscanning was carried out, said: "We
OL,17,Fare pleased and excited to have worked
OL,18,Fas part of this multidisciplinary
OL,19,Fproject.
